caption: So, this KFC is a mixed bag. If you order from them on seamless, you might get the correct order. But I've gotten literally someone else's complete meal before and didn't realize it until the delivery person was long gone. If you go in, you'll get the right food but 50/50 whoever is behind the counter is going to act like your very existence annoys them. If you go through the drive through, they are get it right every time and are very very pleasant. So, do with this what you will. The food is always good though so you'll at least get what you paid for assuming you get what you paid for.
